graph TD
  A[Start] --> B[Input Invoice & Payment Term]
  B --> C[Retrieve Custom Fields]
  C --> D[Calculate Total Amount]
  D --> E[Calculate Discount Based on Rate]
  E --> F[Determine Early Payment Date]
  F --> G{Early Payment?}
  G -->|Yes| H[Apply Early Payment Discount]
  G -->|No| I[Proceed with Standard Payment Date]
  
  H --> J[Create First Installment]
  I --> J
  J --> K[Create Remaining Installments]
  K --> L[Construct Payment Schedule]
  L --> M[Return Payment Schedule]
  M --> Z[End]

